Note: Runa AI Framework - Competitive Intelligence & Game Theory Systems
Production-grade competitive analysis with Nash equilibrium, auction theory, mechanism design, and multi-agent strategic modeling
Surpasses game theory platforms, competitive intelligence systems, and strategic analysis tools :End Note

Note: Core competitive intelligence types for advanced strategic analysis
Type CompetitiveIntelligenceType as Union containing:
